  "title": "Financial Advisor",
  "description": "<p><strong>Financial Advisor</strong><br /><strong>TVG Management Pte. Ltd.</strong><br /><strong>Singapore📍 |Financial Services 💼</strong></p><p><br />TVG Management is expanding our advisory team and is looking for motivated individuals who are interested in building a long-term career in financial advisory, with structured development and clear progression pathways.</p><p><br />This role is suitable for professionals from finance, banking, insurance, business development, or client-facing roles, as well as individuals seeking a career switch into financial services.</p><p><br /><strong>Key Responsibilities :</strong></p><ul><li>Provide personalised financial planning solutions to clients, including protection, wealth accumulation, retirement, and legacy planning.</li><li>Build and maintain long-term client relationships.</li><li>Conduct financial reviews and needs analysis.</li><li>Participate in training, coaching, and professional development programmes.</li><li>Work collaboratively within a team environment to achieve individual and group targets.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong>:</p><ul><li>Minimum Diploma qualification (Degree holders welcome).</li><li>Strong communication and interpersonal skills.</li><li>Self-motivated, disciplined, and willing to learn.</li><li>Comfortable engaging with clients and building relationships.</li><li>Prior experience in finance, banking, insurance, sales, or business development is an advantage but not mandatory.</li><li>Entry level to experienced candidates are welcome</li><li>Full training provided for candidates without prior advisory experience</li></ul><p><strong>What We Offer : </strong></p><ul><li>Structured training and mentorship programme.</li><li>Clear career progression and leadership development pathway.</li><li>Supportive team culture and professional environment.</li><li>Flexibility in managing your own schedule and client portfolio.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><br /></p>",
